					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">If you have an active area wider than 256 pixels (and you really do need one if you scroll horizontally) you absolutely need 16-bit coordinates to keep track of positions properly. Anything else will be a hack, and probably not worth the 1-byte saved per object.</div>

